{"tid":2393642,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"GME 128 招人夾netflix","createTime":"2021-02-03T14:44:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T14:52:10.000Z","uid":15987,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"remark":"[gold]【警告】[/gold]管理團隊最近收到數宗會員舉報，指有騙徒私下聯絡留下聯絡方式之會員，冒充「樓主」身份並要求進行交易，然後在收款後失去聯絡。我們在此呼籲會員提高警覺，切勿輕易留下個人聯絡方法，並務必對未知聯絡人進行身份確認。","replies":[{"pid":"91d5d91920cb771a2c3d7df721f0e8872d81f8a7","tid":2393642,"uid":15987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T14:44:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61a55303319c32cd6cfc4617d01c2a263f1034cf","tid":2393642,"uid":15987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T14:47:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7921f5d3af4ea0d6075412cfd299ff12de4d86c","tid":2393642,"uid":4780,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T14:48:33.000Z","msg":"乜撚野警告<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"680b0c3feb531927255dc2ae3cbee386c4129e50","tid":2393642,"uid":15987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T14:48:53.000Z","msg":"No one is selling at these prices. Sure, maybe a few scared folk who don't know any better. Maybe they trigger a few stop losses. Maybe some margins get called. But it's not enough. Say it with me:<br />\n<br />\nPRICE DOESN'T MATTER<br />\n<br />\nWHAT?!<br />\n<br />\nYou heard me. 30cent GME? No problem.<br />\n<br />\nThey don't need a low price, they need your shares. If 10 people sell at 30c cents, and that's the only market activity, it's a &quot;30 cent stock&quot; but Melvin only netted ten shares. They are still fucked. They aren't buying 50 million shares at 30c, nor $100, nor $300, and that's their problem. It's an availability issue. Sometimes it's ALSO a price issue (too high for them) but primarily it's the availability."},{"pid":"7dc43e6e16af023d07d0b6f7a3163a0a97cb28c5","tid":2393642,"uid":249883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T14:49:29.000Z","msg":"Citibank都set唔到3萬，shit!"},{"pid":"d9b3c9052270aa3a497fc8ad9b4de7274bce6ee8","tid":2393642,"uid":105176,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T14:49:33.000Z","msg":"Tg: hugo1991 我係樓主 快啲搵我交易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16bc461e4458287da22739b75aeef740834f64c7","tid":2393642,"uid":15987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7dc43e6e16af023d07d0b6f7a3163a0a97cb28c5","tid":2393642,"uid":249883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T14:49:29.000Z","msg":"Citibank都set唔到3萬，shit!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T14:49:39.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"490b6e845e9a92457c655b2fc2191cebb12be136","tid":2393642,"uid":84303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7921f5d3af4ea0d6075412cfd299ff12de4d86c","tid":2393642,"uid":4780,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T14:48:33.000Z","msg":"乜撚野警告<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T14:49:48.000Z","msg":"連尼住都覺得GME係騙局<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa6f7cba946cc5b492d4b638e0c7df87bf4d4087","tid":2393642,"uid":15987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"490b6e845e9a92457c655b2fc2191cebb12be136","tid":2393642,"uid":84303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7921f5d3af4ea0d6075412cfd299ff12de4d86c","tid":2393642,"uid":4780,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T14:48:33.000Z","msg":"乜撚野警告<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T14:49:48.000Z","m